Cell.Data: Danielle Sho might still be alive. In a message to her girlfriend, she said she fled to the station exterior and would be waiting outside the Fitness Center window for a signal - banging on the glass.

Danielle Sho might still be alive. In a message to her girlfriend, she said she fled to the station exterior and would be waiting outside the Fitness Center window for a signal - banging on the glass.

Danielle Sho is actually alive outside the station - though, not for long. Before I left her, she lamented the death of her partner Abby at the hands of the imposter cook. The Cook is still out there on Talos and is a threat to all the remaining crew.

I discovered that Chief Archivist Danielle Sho was actually alive outside the station. The imposter cook, a psychologically unstable volunteer who managed to escape the Neuromod Division, killed her partner, Abigail Foy. He managed to kill multiple staff members on the station and had a special vendetta against the Yu family. Fortunately, I took care of it.
